  "description": "Align Contact Card Title and Email on Contact Page\n\nFix the alignment issue where the contact card title with email appears off-center on the contact page, likely caused by email addresses exceeding available width.\n\nRequirements:\n- Investigate the contact card component to identify layout constraints causing misalignment\n- Implement proper text overflow handling for long email addresses (truncation, ellipsis, or wrapping)\n- Ensure title and email maintain centered alignment regardless of email length\n- Test with various email address lengths (short, medium, very long)\n- Verify responsive behavior across different screen sizes\n- Maintain visual hierarchy between title and email elements\n- Ensure email remains readable and accessible after fix",
